 About Me
Main ek passionate SEO Specialist hoon jise digital space mein 2 saal ka professional experience hai. Mera focus sirf traffic barhane par nahi, balki right audience ko target kar ke business revenue boost karne par hota hai. Main search engine algorithms ko samajhta hoon aur unke mutabiq strategies design karta hoon.

## Core Skills & Expertise
On-Page SEO: Keyword Research, Content Optimization, Meta Tags, URL Structuring, Internal Linking.

Technical SEO: Site Audits, Speed Optimization, Core Web Vitals, XML Sitemaps, Robots.txt.

Off-Page SEO: Link Building, Guest Posting, Competitor Backlink Analysis.

Tools I Use: Google Analytics (GA4), Google Search Console, Ahrefs, SEMrush, Screaming Frog.

Featured Projects (Case Studies)
1. Wrestling Bets Website (Niche: Sports & Betting)
Overview: Ek highly competitive niche (Sports/Betting) mein organic visibility aur traffic ko grow kiya.

My Role & Strategy:

High-intent aur low-competition keywords ko target kiya jin par search volume achha tha.

Informational aur transactional content ki On-Page optimization ki taake user intent match ho.

Strict Google guidelines ko follow karte hue safe Link Building (Backlinks) ki.

Results: Organic traffic mein X% izafa hua aur kai high-volume keywords top pages par rank karne lage. (Yahan aap actual % ya numbers likh sakte hain).

2. IT & Tech Platform
Overview: Ek IT service/blog website ki technical aur structural problems ko sahi kar ke organic reach barhayi.

My Role & Strategy:

Mukammal Technical SEO Audit kiya aur crawlability issues, broken links, aur page speed ko behtar banaya.

Tech blogs ke liye semantic keywords ka use kiya aur content architecture ko standard banaya.

Results: Site ki indexing fast hui, bounce rate kam hua, aur IT-related terms par impressions 2x ho gaye.

